  "instructions": [
    "Preheat a dry skillet over medium heat.",
    "Place stale bread slices in the skillet and toast until lightly golden (2-3 minutes).",
    "Remove bread and set aside.",
    "In the same skillet, add pickled onions and cook for 1 minute until slightly caramelized.",
    "Stir in smoked paprika and garlic powder, then add black pepper.",
    "Return bread to skillet and toss with the onion mixture until evenly coated (1 minute).",
    "Serve immediately while hot and crunchy."
